'''''Christina Yngvesdotter'' Herrström Schildt''' (born ''Herrström'' 23 August 1959<ref>http://www.birthday.se/sok/?f=Christina&l=Herrstr%f6m%20Schildt{{dead link|date=August 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> in [[Lidingö]], [[Sweden]]) is a Swedish [[author]] and [[screenwriter]]. She has been married to [[Peter Schildt]].<ref>http://www.stadsbiblioteket.nu/tusen-ganger-starkare/</ref> She has written among the [[children's literature|children's books]] ''[[Ebba & Didrik]]'', ''[[Glappet]]'' and ''[[Tusen gånger starkare]]''<ref>http://libris.kb.se/hitlist?d=libris&q=f%c3%b6rf%3a(Herrstr%c3%b6m%2c+Christina%2c+1959-)&f=simp&spell=true&hist=true&p=1</ref> and she has also written the films/TV series based on these books (''Glappet'' was first a TV series but she wrote a book based on it). She has also written other films and TV series.
